                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7508" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1176</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1681 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">弃车保帅：腾讯持续发放“证券股利”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Retreat for the sake of advancing,break up but don&#39;t give up cooperation ——Tencent continues to dole out securities dividends</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">汪金祥，林思艳，范舒雯，何子昕</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">腾讯控股有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">腾讯；分红；财产股利；证券股利</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Tencent, dividends, property dividends, securities dividends</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022年10月25日，党的二十大报告全文公布，其中指出要加强反垄断和反不正当竞争，破除地方保护和行政性垄断，依法规范和引导资本健康发展。早在2021年，互联网龙头企业腾讯就因为反垄断、游戏行业新规政策的出台屡屡受罚，成为政府反垄断监管的重点对象。2021年腾讯净利润增幅为近十年最低，可见腾讯发展大不如前。在加强反垄断调查的背景下，互联网企业如何寻求突破至关重要。本文主要从腾讯派发证券股利事件展开，探讨腾讯实施证券股利的动因以及对市场反应的影响，分析腾讯这种丢军保帅的行为是否是明智之举？本文旨在帮助学生学习财务管理及企业利润分配中分红的相关知识，同时，为腾讯及同行业其它上市公司、投资者和监管部门提供借鉴与帮助。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> On October 25, 2022, the full text of the report of the Party&#39;s 20th National Congress was released, which pointed out that we should strengthen anti-monopoly and anti-unfair competition, break local protection and administrative monopolies, and regulate and guide the healthy development of capital according to law. As early as 2021, the Internet leading enterprise Tencent was repeatedly punished because of the introduction of new regulations and policies in the anti-monopoly and game industry, and became the focus of the government&#39;s anti-monopoly supervision. In 2021, Tencent&#39;s net profit growth rate was the lowest in nearly ten years, which shows that Tencent&#39;s development is not as good as before. In the context of strengthening anti-monopoly investigations, how Internet companies seek breakthroughs is crucial. This paper mainly starts from the incident of Tencent&#39;s distribution of securities dividends, discusses the motivation of Tencent&#39;s implementation of securities dividends and its impact on the market reaction, and analyzes whether Tencent&#39;s behavior of losing the army and protecting the commander is wise. This paper aims to help students learn about financial management and dividends in corporate profit distribution, and at the same time, provide reference and help for Tencent and other listed companies in the same industry, investors and regulatory authorities.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">股利政策；财产股利；证券股利</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-09</td>
                            </tr>
